Initialize local Axon config, env, and compose assets

Usage
  axon setup init [OPTIONS]

Options
  --mcp-host <MCP_HOST>            MCP HTTP bind host written to AXON_MCP_HTTP_HOST
  --mcp-port <MCP_PORT>            MCP HTTP bind port written to AXON_MCP_HTTP_PORT
  --auth-mode <AUTH_MODE>          MCP auth mode. Bearer generates/requires AXON_MCP_HTTP_TOKEN; OAuth requires Google OAuth vars
  --mcp-token <MCP_TOKEN>          Static bearer token for AXON_MCP_HTTP_TOKEN
  --oauth-public-url <OAUTH_PUBLIC_URL>
                                   Public URL for OAuth metadata and callbacks
  --google-client-id <GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID>
                                   Google OAuth client ID
  --google-client-secret <GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET>
                                   Google OAuth client secret
  --auth-admin-email <AUTH_ADMIN_EMAIL>
                                   Admin email allowed to complete OAuth auth
  --tavily-api-key <TAVILY_API_KEY>
                                   Tavily API key for search/research
  --github-token <GITHUB_TOKEN>    GitHub token for higher-rate GitHub ingest
  --reddit-client-id <REDDIT_CLIENT_ID>
                                   Reddit client ID for Reddit ingest
  --reddit-client-secret <REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET>
                                   Reddit client secret for Reddit ingest
  -h, --help                       Print help
